originalText: ::Familiar acid encircles the cuttlesnail. The creature is stuck, and it doesn't have enough strength to free itself. From time to time, the snail would try to wiggle away the sticky goo, with little to no effect. You approach it to get a better look.::
::Use the other hand to break free.::
::Your hand is stuck. Yanking it causes you great pain and no desired results.::

::Startled by the sight of what's happening, you promptly start pushing through the jelly tissue around your trapped hand. For a brief moment, you manage to relieve the strangle hold off of your right hand. This quickly backfires as now your left hand is stuck, perhaps even worse than the other one was previously. In panic, you attempt to free the left hand, and before you know it, both hands are now stuck inside the cuttlesnail.::

::The fear of getting stuck consumes you, as you launch your head inside with everything you've got. Your sharp teeth cut through the snail with breeze. In process, you start to swallow some of its organs. Swinging left and right with your jaw is progressively becoming more exhausting, as there seems to be no end to it all. Now, your entire upper body is inside the snail, and at this point its hard to make distinction between what's acidic sludge and what are the snail's remains that ensnare you.::
::You devour what's left of it, chewing most of the humid stains away from your limbs. It all tastes bitter-sweet now. Fatigued, you drop down on your knees.::
